            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            
            <p>Enigma Footwear</p>
            
            <p>Enigma Footwear is a small shoe boutique located in Beverly Hills, California. Our store is located in the heart of Los Angeles and offers a variety of one of a kind shoe designs. Enigma Footwear is exclusively sold at our location and is guaranteed to transform any outfit.</p><!--Short description of the company-->
            
            <h2>Target audience</h2>
            
            <p>Enigma Footwear offers shoes for both men and women, and is for anyone looking to expand their shoe collection and elevate their look.</p>
            
